; The in-memory MongoDB (Minimongo) — a collection store with mutations, cursors, and a reactive
; observe engine. Mutations synchronously emit change events (the "simulated change stream");
; observe/observeChanges recompute off them via the pure matcher/diff core — no Eio, no polling, a
; mutation IS the event. Pure (Bson + query), so it cross-compiles to JavaScript. This is the
; default backend for dev and test. Inline tests live in ../test (this library stays dep-free).

(library
 (name minimongo)
 (public_name fennec-mongo.minimongo)
 (libraries bson query))
